print("\nLet me reconsider the problem:")
print("We want subsequences where consecutive elements differ by exactly k")
print("So if we have a subsequence ending in value v, the next element should be v+k or v-k")
print("But we process elements one by one, so for element 'num' we check if it can extend a previous sequence")
